snippet.title: Eiyu*Senki Gold - A New Conquest - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
In the ancient far Eastern country of Zipang, a storm is brewing. The country enjoys a period of peace and its unique culture flourishes thanks to the isolationism imposed by the great Ancient Hero, Yamato Takeru. But the heart of one lone hero, Masamune Date, burns with the fire of ambition in this seemingly content land.  After coming across an young man, void of all his memories, she uses him to put her plans into motion to challenge to Takeru, force open the country's borders, and begin the conquest of the world!

Developed by Tenco
Published by JAST USA

Follow JAST USA for more information:
